<%- include('./partials/html-head') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.css" />
<%- include('./partials/nav') %>

<main>
  <h1>Welcome to Habitton</h1>
  <% if (user?.profile.avatar) { %>
    <div>
      <img
        src="<%= user.profile.avatar %>"
        alt="<%= user.profile.name %> avatar"
      />
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <% if (user) { %> 
    <div class="links">
      <a href="/habits">See Your Habits</a>
    </div>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="/habits/new">Make A Habit</a>
    </div>
  <% } else { %> 
    <p>Habitton is an app to help you make new daily habits. You can make habits and record completing them each day.</p>

    <p>Keep in mind S.M.A.R.T. goals: your habit should be Specific, Measurable, Attainable, Relevant, and Timely. "Be productive" is not specific -- try "</p>
  <% } %> 
</main>

